OL,3,CInvestigation into death of man in
OL,4,CLeicester transferred to Metropolitan
OL,5,CPolice
OL,7,FAn investigation into the death of a
OL,8,Fman whose body was found in a van in
OL,9,FLeicester has been transferred to the
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police.
OL,12,FPolice were called to a car park in
OL,13,FGarden Street just after 5.30pm on
OL,14,FWednesday (27 May) by a member of the
OL,15,Fpublic reporting concern about the
OL,16,Fcondition of the vehicle.
OL,18,FWhen officers forced entry to the van,
OL,19,Fthe body of a man was found inside.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
