OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1780323077
OL,3,CInvestigation into death of man in
OL,4,CLeicester transferred to Metropolitan
OL,5,CPolice
OL,7,FEnquiries surrounding the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of the man's death were
OL,9,Fundertaken by the East Midlands
OL,10,FSpecial Operations Unit (EMSOU) and
OL,11,Fsupported by officers from
OL,12,FLeicestershire Police.
OL,14,FFollowing a search at a property in
OL,15,FHounslow yesterday (Saturday), the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police has now taken
OL,17,Fresponsibility for the investigation.
